PMID== 6258779
TI  == induction of epstein-barr virus antigens in human lymphoblastoid p3hr-1 cells with culture fluid of fusobacterium nucleatum.
AB  == epstein-barr virus-associated early antigen and viral capsid antigen were efficiently induced in human lymphoblastoid p3hr-1 cells with culture fluid of fusobacterium nucleatum, a member of the indigenous microbial flora of the human  host. this finding may suggest a new approach to assess the possible role of the  "cofactor(s)" in the etiology of epstein-barr virus-related diseases.
